title: Swim Instructor Interview
Application Type: I interviewed at YMCA of Greater Rochester
Interview Descriptions: Very Straightforward, they ask questions about experience with teaching and swimming. I first had a phone screening call and then in person interview. They were very nice! It was a good process, everyone was friendly!
Interview Questions: What is your experience with swimming?

title: Member Service Representative Interview
Application Type: I applied online. The process took 4 weeks. I interviewed at YMCA of Greater Rochester (Rochester, NY) in Jan 2020
Interview Descriptions: Interview itself was very simple. I wore dress jeans and a flowy top and fit in well. Questions had to do about how my p[previous roles would help me and if I had worked in customer service
Interview Questions: If you had to lead a tour of our building how would you choose what to show and information to tell?
